National_City.Oak Park, San Diego:
Oak Park is a neighborhood of the Southeast region of San Diego, California. It is currently being transformed into a new hub for urban culture due to its diversity and adjacency to South Park and SDSU.


== Geography ==
The neighborhood's borders are defined by Euclid Avenue to the west, Chollas Parkway/Streamview Drive/College Avenue to the north, and State Route 94 to the southeast. Oak Park map


== Economy ==
Oak Park is located 4 miles (6 km) from San Diego State University.
